          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-row">
        <h2 class="about-row__title">What this Site is for</h2>
        <div class="about-row__body">
          <p>
            The Site provides general information about <strong>Perennial Web Studio</strong>, operated by
            <strong>Heather Mielke</strong>, including marketing for brochure-style and small multi-page websites, pricing
