            create a client relationship until we have explicitly agreed to one in writing (for example, through a signed
            proposal, statement of work, or contract).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-row">
        <h2 class="about-row__title">Intellectual property</h2>
        <div class="about-row__body">
          <p>
            Text, layout, graphics, and other materials on the Site (except where noted) are owned by or licensed to
            Perennial Web Studio and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may view and share links to
            the Site for personal or non-commercial reference. You may not copy, scrape, or redistribute Site content for
            commercial use, train machine learning models on our content without permission, or remove notices or branding.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Portfolio and client work:</strong> Project screenshots or descriptions shown here are displayed with
            permission where required and remain subject to any separate agreements with those clients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-row">
        <h2 class="about-row__title">Acceptable use</h2>
        <div class="about-row__body">
          <p>
            You agree not to use the Site in any way that is unlawful, harassing, or intended to damage, overload, or
            interfere with our systems or security. You may not attempt unauthorized access to any part of the Site, other
            users, or our infrastructure. We may suspend or block access if we reasonably believe these terms are being
            violated.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-row">
        <h2 class="about-row__title">Contact forms and communications</h2>
        <div class="about-row__body">
          <p>
            If you submit information through a contact or quote form, you represent that the information is accurate to the
            best of your knowledge and that you have the right to share it. Do not submit confidential or sensitive personal
            data unless we have agreed to a secure channel. How we handle personal information is described in our
            <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-row">
        <h2 class="about-row__title">Third-party links and tools</h2>
        <div class="about-row__body">
          <p>
            The Site may link to third-party websites, fonts, analytics, or embeds. We do not control those services and are
            not responsible for their content or practices. Your use of third-party sites is governed by their own terms and
            policies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-row">
        <h2 class="about-row__title">Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
        <div class="about-row__body">
          <p>
            The Site and its content are provided <strong>“as is”</strong> and <strong>“as available.”</strong> We strive for
